<subSubSection pageId="7" pageNumber="86" type="dispersal potential">
<paragraph pageId="7" pageNumber="86">Dispersal potential.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="7" pageNumber="86">These beetles are macropterous and capable of flight. They are moderately swift and agile runners.</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection pageId="7" pageNumber="86" type="way of life">
<paragraph pageId="7" pageNumber="86">Way of life.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="7" pageNumber="86">The adult holotype was collected in a flight intercept trap in the rainforest understory. The adult holotype was active in November, at the end of the dry season.</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
